attributes.Long form description: The student is to assemble the utility cart. First, the student attaches the legs and screws it, then attaches it to the base frame. Next, the student puts the grid tray in the middle of the legs and uses the bracket, bolt, and hexagon cap nut to assemble the utility cart. Lastly, the student assembles the wheels to the base frame.
